{"tid":1280780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺好多人都唔識法律","createTime":"2019-07-03T05:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T15:30:11.000Z","uid":73392,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e9233d4ad516c69f60d596210a61aece87fb7b","tid":1280780,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:44:45.000Z","msg":"其實將所有電子野，電話，電腦用垃圾袋包起，收賣去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好收係屋企</span>，去公園埋左去又好，放去電錶房又好，唔好攞去親戚朋友度，佢地比狗大到，佢地又冇衝嘅話推你出黎，你就仆街，搜查令同一case只可以上門搜一次，果一之搜唔到，根本就過左關<br />\n<br />\n真係比狗上門嘅話，唔洗我教啦，大把post有講，咩都話我冇野講，9 成都入唔到你<br />\n<br />\n佢地要極大嘅證據，先入到你，唔好咁on9認，仲有就算咩證據都齊，都有可能因為d犬嘅失誤而搞到證據缺失，而告唔到，唔好灰機放棄，希望係有嘅，而且仲有大<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企人做過最前線+召集人+比曬電話電腦+冇密碼+有曬高登tg對話記錄+不誠實使用電腦仲未比廢武功  都沒事，正確d黎講連charge都落唔到，就放左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89783ff1cff98c4f276713110db0e8cc711af525","tid":1280780,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea9dbb344084dcef17b0dc7a3c224eda4f907871","tid":1280780,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1490cd2bc2bdae5d58cb6171e16efb33d2062c7","tid":1280780,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c64b9f81d3c460a98328659423a25d3120691b1b","tid":1280780,"uid":197404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e09debae2664c0d7c4df6e6f955fc79313f3877","tid":1280780,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"做得召集人先易無事<br />\n<br />\nLayman要小心謹慎保護自己<br />\n唔好留住何證據"},{"pid":"a50903479f42d921c14bbf8fc867214315cf413e","tid":1280780,"uid":65354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:47:56.000Z","msg":"最緊要shut the fuck up<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.b